      "audio_script": "Listen to 2 Thessalonians. Paul encourages persecuted believers with God's justice and Christ's return. He clarifies that the day of the Lord has not already come and warns against deception. He calls the church to stand firm in apostolic teaching and practice disciplined, responsible life.",
