      "audio_script": "Eschatology should stabilize, not sensationalize. Truth and disciplined work protect community health while believers await Christ.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "themes",
      "sequence": 5,
      "audio_script": "Key themes include perseverance, discernment, faithfulness, discipline, and patient hope.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "sequence": 6,
      "audio_script": "Review question: What does Paul say about the man of lawlessness in 2 Thessalonians 2? Answer: he will exalt himself above every god and object of worship, proclaiming himself to be God, before the Lord Jesus destroys him at his coming.",
