    }
  ],
  "segments": [
    {
      "type": "orientation",
      "sequence": 1,
      "audio_script": "Paul instructs Timothy to guard doctrine and shape church life according to the gospel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "reading",
      "sequence": 2,
      "audio_script": "Listen to 1 Timothy 1-3. Paul commands Timothy to confront false teaching and preserve love from a pure heart. He celebrates mercy shown to him as a former persecutor. He urges prayer for all people and gives qualifications for overseers and deacons so God's household displays truth.",
