      "audio_script": "Listen to Hebrews 5-10. Jesus is the eternal priest in the order of Melchizedek. The writer warns against spiritual immaturity and urges diligence in hope. Christ mediates a better covenant with better promises. His sacrifice is final and sufficient, cleansing conscience and opening true access to God. Believers are urged not to shrink back but to endure in faith.",
