      "audio_script": "Listen to 1 Peter 3-5. Peter gives relational guidance for households and community life, calling believers to bless when reviled and be ready to explain their hope. He frames suffering through Christ's once-for-all sacrifice and resurrection victory. Elders are charged to shepherd willingly, and all are urged to humble themselves, cast anxieties on God, and resist the devil.",
