      "type": "reading",
      "sequence": 2,
      "audio_script": "Listen to Revelation 4-8:13. John sees God's throne and ceaseless worship. A sealed scroll appears, and only the slain yet living Lamb is worthy to open it. As seals are opened, judgments unfold, while God's people are marked and a vast multitude from every nation worships the Lamb. Trumpet judgments begin, showing partial but serious warnings on the earth.",
